{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "emily.chen", "message": "Hi team, I've been looking into the McKinsey report that suggests over 50 million in-person visits could be converted to virtual visits. This presents a massive opportunity for us to leverage.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "john_doe", "message": "That sounds promising, Emily. Given this, how should we tweak our marketing strategy for Q4 2026 to promote our virtual services?", "create_at": 1620500100000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "marketing", "channel": "market_analysis", "user": "emily.chen", "message": "I believe we need to emphasize the convenience, cost-effectiveness, and advanced technology of our virtual services. This could include showcasing our AI capabilities. In fact, based on current trends, by 2027, we expect about 35% of our consultations to be AI-assisted.", "create_at": 1620500200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "ai_research", "channel": "ai_strategy", "user": "sarah_smith", "message": "That's a great point, Emily. Our team is working on enhancing our AI capabilities. The integration of AI will not only improve our services but also position us as a leading innovator in the virtual healthcare industry.", "create_at": 1620500300000}}
